item.title: Moparscape cache
item.dc:creator: @TimMane TimMane
item.description:
@TimMane wrote:

Sorry i know this is an old topic but i had this same problem
but now i fixed it and its now working

to fix this goto C:\WINDOWS.mpr_file_store_32
and copy any picture file you have on your pc to that folder and rename it to mopar.jpg

you can now start using the client btw the picture you put in your cache folder will be the title screen the one you see during login

Btw the link to download the cache is down doesnt work i find a link on google for the cache files
